subtitleNullable: Historical Daily summary data of Companies listed under NSE
descriptionNullable:
This dataset has been created using nsepy package. Once the dataset is fully updated this has historical data about companies listed in NSE.

Historical data from 1996 till the last calendar year is available in *.DB format. Each DB file (NSE-Data-1996.db) has a table with the name "NSEYYYY" (NSE1996) format.

Users can use the sqlite3 package to read these db files.

The latest year data will be available in parquet file format. 

The usual update frequency is weekly. We are trying to update each stock at least once a week.

Disclaimer: We are trying to make this dataset as accurate as possible. This dataset is created only for educational purposes.
